{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aether Echoes Podcasting Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #3467eb;\n            --secondary-blue: #6a91f0;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-dark: #1a1a1a;\n            --accent-color: #f0e68c; /* A muted gold for accent */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-dark);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: -50px;\n            width: 300px;\n            height: 300px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            filter: blur(40px);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-top: 3px solid var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item img {\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 120px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 4px solid var(--brand-blue);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(52, 103, 235, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-blue) 0%, var(--brand-blue) 100%);\n            border-radius: 0;\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--background-dark);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #d4c46a; /* Slightly darker accent */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-dark);\n            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.8em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .podcast-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Aether Echoes</h1>\n        <p>Journeys through sound, where stories ignite and ideas resonate. Discover your next auditory adventure.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>Our Vision</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n                At Aether Echoes, we believe in the power of audio to connect, inform, and inspire. We curate a diverse collection of podcasts, pushing the boundaries of storytelling and sonic exploration. From intimate conversations to grand narratives, we bring you voices that matter.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"podcasts\">\n            <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/120/3467eb/ffffff?text=AE\" alt=\"Podcast Icon 1\">\n                    <h3>Cosmic Canvas</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the intersection of art and the universe, one episode at a time.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/120/6a91f0/ffffff?text=AE\" alt=\"Podcast Icon 2\">\n                    <h3>Whispers of History</h3>\n                    <p>Unearthing forgotten tales and overlooked moments that shaped our world.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/120/3467eb/ffffff?text=AE\" alt=\"Podcast Icon 3\">\n                    <h3>The Mind's Labyrinth</h3>\n                    <p>A deep dive into psychology, philosophy, and the human condition.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/120/6a91f0/ffffff?text=AE\" alt=\"Podcast Icon 4\">\n                    <h3>Future Forward</h3>\n                    <p>Conversations with innovators shaping the technologies and societies of tomorrow.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Join the Conversation</h2>\n        <p>Subscribe to our network and never miss an echo. Find us on all major podcasting platforms.</p>\n        <a href=\"#subscribe\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Shows</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Aether Echoes Podcasting Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>A Network by <a href=\"#\">Echo Creators</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}